Sharon est sauvée !

1508
02:03:12,900 --> 02:03:14,600
Il reste vingt minutes.

1509
02:03:14,700 --> 02:03:16,500
Alors Banania !

1510
02:03:17,400 --> 02:03:19,400
Tu n'as pas l'air ravi.

1511
